g src=\"https://hanoicomputercdn.com/media/lib/32316_C930e1.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></span></p><h3 style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\">ĐƯỢC CHỨNG NHẬN CHO DOANH NGHIỆP</h3><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 700;\">C930e</span>&nbsp;được chứng nhận tương thích với Skype for Business và Cisco Jabber™, và tích hợp nâng cao với BlueJeans, Broadsoft, LifeSize Cloud, Vidyo và Zoom.</span></p><p style=\"color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;; font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"https://hanoicomputercdn.com/media/lib/32316_C930e2.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"border-width: initial; border-style: none; max-width: 100%; height: auto; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"></span></p><h3 style=\"font-weight: 700; color: rgb(34, 34, 34); font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Arial, sans-serif, &quot;Apple Color Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Emoji&quot;, &quot;Segoe UI Symbol&quot;;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12pt; font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif;\">C